A "{{ball}}" [ball](https://github.com/jbrudvik/baller).

## Install

    $ git clone https://github.com/{{username}}/{{ball}}.git
    $ {{ball}}/install

`{{ball}}/files` contains the list of files that will be installed to your home directory. If any of these files already exist, they will be backed up as `~/<file>.<timestamp>.bak`.

## Update

    $ {{ball}}/update

Update to the latest {{ball}} changes.

## Uninstall

    $ {{ball}}/uninstall

Will restore to previous file backups if present.

## Remove backups

    $ {{ball}}/remove-backups

Remove all backup files. Cannot be undone!
